00:00:59.453 --> 00:01:01.417
ROB BAEDEKER: Hello.

00:01:01.417 --> 00:01:02.570
AUDIENCE: Hi.

00:01:02.570 --> 00:01:05.034
ROB BAEDEKER: Oh good,
we're off to a good start.

00:01:05.034 --> 00:01:05.950
Thanks for coming out.

00:01:05.950 --> 00:01:07.699
We're the authors of
"What To Talk About."

00:01:07.699 --> 00:01:11.550
